---

<section class="w-full pt-8 pb-16 flex flex-col gap-6">
  {/* Header */}
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2 border-b border-accent-600 pb-2">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-accent-800 font-heading">Nosso Canal no YouTube</h2>
    <a
      href="https://www.youtube.com/@LABELUuefs"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="shrink-0 text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-800 uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center gap-1"
    >
      VER CANAL <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  {/* Content */}
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-stretch bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
    
    {/* Video — full width on mobile, 3/5 on desktop */}
    <div class="w-full md:w-3/5 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-md bg-black">
      <div class="relative w-full" style="padding-top: 56.25%;">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/PwDJJGOYVSE"
          title="YouTube video player"
          frameborder="0"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
          allowfullscreen
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full border-none"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Info card — full width on mobile, 2/5 on desktop */}
    <div class="w-full md:w-2/5 flex flex-col gap-4 justify-center">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 rounded-full bg-accent-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl shrink-0 shadow-sm">
          L
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-title leading-tight">Labelu - Laboratório de História</h3>
          <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-body">Canal Oficial</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-body text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
        Acompanhe nossos debates, seminários, defesas e conteúdos exclusivos produzidos pelo laboratório. Inscreva-se para ficar por dentro de tudo o que acontece no Labelu e fortalecer a memória da luta de classes!
      </p>

      <div>
        <a
          href="https://www.youtube.com/@LABELUuefs"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full sm:w-auto px-5 py-2.5 bg-[#FF0000] text-white rounded-md font-bold hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors gap-2 shadow-sm text-sm sm:text-base"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M21.582,6.186c-0.23-0.86-0.908-1.538-1.768-1.768C18.254,4,12,4,12,4S5.746,4,4.186,4.418c-0.86,0.23-1.538,0.908-1.768,1.768C2,7.746,2,12,2,12s0,4.254,0.418,5.814c0.23,0.86,0.908,1.538,1.768,1.768C5.746,20,12,20,12,20s6.254,0,7.814-0.418c0.86-0.23,1.538-0.908,1.768-1.768C22,16.254,22,12,22,12S22,7.746,21.582,6.186z M9.667,14.667V9.333L15.333,12L9.667,14.667z"/>
          </svg>
          Inscrever-se no Canal
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
